# Welcome to MDX! This is a **sample MDX file**. You can mix Markdown with JSX components here. ## Example Components ### Heading Components

This is an HTML heading inside MDX

This is a custom React component usage. ### Images ![Sample Image](/path/to/image.jpg) ### Lists - List item 1 - List item 2 - List item 3 ### Code Blocks ```jsx const MyComponent = ({ text }) => (

{text}

); ``` ### Links [Visit OpenAI](https://www.openai.com) ### Embedded JSX

This is JSX embedded inside MDX.
